What is it?

SlackinKrakens AddressBook is a desktop application address book for linux based systems. The address book allows you to save contacts and their relevant information all in the comfort of a web-based interface. You can create new address books, add contacts to them, delete contacts from them, and delete entire address books

How to Install

These instructions are for Linux based systems.

1.) Make sure you have Python3 installed
    * On a debian-based system run "sudo apt install python3"
2.) Make sure you have the python pip package manager installed
    * On a debian-based system run "sudo apt install python3-pip"
3.) Make sure you are in the "SlackinKrakens_AddressBook" folder and run the application
    * Run "sudo bash run.sh" to install the requirements and run the application
